                <DefaultStyle/>
                <ITEXT CH="With arpeg­gio, notes of the se­lected chord are trig­gered in­di­vid­u­ally. The se­lected type de­fines how should be the notes or­dered. Some types can be RE­SET to their ini­tial po­si­tion – use two different clock sources for TRIGGER and RS/NX to create interesting patterns. Other types are re­peat­ing the same se­quence un­til NEXT is trig­gered."/>
