            <StoryText>
                <DefaultStyle/>
                <ITEXT CH="Cal­i­bra­tion, CV map­ping and all other at­tributes are per­sisted be­tween restarts of the mod­ule. To re­set their val­ues, hold the RE­SET but­ton while pow­er­ing the mod­ule on."/>
                <trail/>
            </StoryText>
        </PAGEOBJECT>
